Enum BinaryPrefix

  • Object
    • Enum<BinaryPrefix>
      • BinaryPrefix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<BinaryPrefix>, Prefix

    public enum BinaryPrefix
extends Enum<BinaryPrefix>
implements Prefix

    This class provides support for common binary prefixes to be used by units.

    Since:
    2.0
    Version:
    1.3, April 20, 2018
    Author:
